214
00:18:56,460 --> 00:18:57,920
 Bitno da se spasimo.

215
00:18:57,920 --> 00:19:00,940
 Vi ćete gori biti sveti.

216
00:19:00,940 --> 00:19:04,040
 I ne znam jeste ikad razmišljali,

217
00:19:04,040 --> 00:19:07,860
 kad dođete u nebo, a u nebo ne ulazi ništa nečisto,

218
00:19:07,860 --> 00:19:10,440
 vi ćete gori biti sveti.

219
00:19:10,440 --> 00:19:12,100
 Kako je to prekrasno.

220
00:19:13,640 --> 00:19:16,640
 E možete zaklopiti oči na pola minuta.

221
00:19:16,640 --> 00:19:17,560
 Zaklopite oči.

222
00:19:17,560 --> 00:19:21,640
 I želim da sad zamolite duha sve.

223
00:19:21,640 --> 00:19:23,920
 Duš sveti ja te molim, pokaži ovim ljudima

224
00:19:23,920 --> 00:19:27,260
