225
00:19:27,260 --> 00:19:30,200
 E dopustite duh svetom da vam pokaže

226
00:19:30,200 --> 00:19:32,560
 vašu svetu sličicu u nebu.

227
00:19:32,560 --> 00:19:32,940
 Evo.

228
00:19:32,940 --> 00:19:41,460
 Slobodno si stavite areolu iznad glave.

229
00:19:41,460 --> 00:19:43,920
