230
00:19:43,920 --> 00:19:54,380
 Super.

231
00:19:54,380 --> 00:19:56,960
 Znači, svi ćete biti sveti.

232
00:19:56,960 --> 00:19:58,560
 I taj proces

233
00:19:58,560 --> 00:20:01,560
